snippet.title: Wildcard | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Welcome to Wildcard

Wildcard is a first-of-its-kind hybrid of real-time strategy, arena-based MOBAs, and collectible card games, all powered by cutting-edge technology. Witness the pulse-pounding mix of action and strategy in our NEW trailer.

Learn more at https://www.wildcardgame.com/
